  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Application Engineer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Application support and setup of motion control system, machine vision system, signal and control devices, used in motion control products and automation equipment</li>\n  <li>Design of electrical schematic diagram, single line diagram, cable harness and build, for motion controller systems, device and sensors, used in Industrial automation machine and equipment</li>\n  <li>Perform DOE for risk mitigation and feasibility studies on design concept</li>\n  <li>Creation of Bill of Material of cables assembly and electrical component used in project</li>\n  <li>Review and guides the development of product manual and application notes for new products/applications</li>\n  <li>Evaluate and recommend product / solutions for new applications according to customer’s specification</li>\n  <li>Understand and help to resolve application issues encountered in projects and by customer</li>\n  <li>Work with team to fomulate work instructions</li>\n  <li>Machine commisioning in factory/customer Site</li>\n  <li>Ensure design meets project required milestone and timeline</li>\n  <li>Provide training to customer </li>\n  <li>Overseas travel is required with short notice period</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably with 1-2 Year(s) of working experience in Industrial Automation, Semiconductor or any other related field/industry is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Applicants without experience but with good learning ability are welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>Required Knowledge: Power sizing, power distribution, motion control (advantage)</li>\n  <li>Required Skill(s): AutoCAD, Solidworks, Motion control software (advantage)</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and analytical skills, energetic and willing to work hard </li>\n  <li>Ability to prioritize and multi-task in a fast-paced environment </li>\n  <li>Responsible, Positive Attitude and able to work well as a team  </li>\n  <li>Possess good initiative and good critical thinking skill to solve issue at root cause level</li>\n</ul>",
